reviewText:
Another great quest I've came across recently.
It's that rare type of quest with logical and non-mind♥♥♥♥ing puzzles.

Another pros:
great sci-fi plot about time-travelling;
amazing ambient music;
absolutely brilliant pop art drawing style;
easy achievements ;)Cons:
tablet-port controls may be a bit clumsy;
display adjustments don't save due to some unknown reasons
All in all, despite controls and port issues it's a solid 10/10, finished in one breath, would recommend to anyone who loves quests and sci-fi.
